ont-size: xx-large;\">辛亥革命因為新軍倒戈，國民黨失去大陸亦係因為高級將領倒戈，雖然我地都知班黑狗唔敢反支共，但支共永遠唔會相信佢地架，如果我地唔睇清呢層關係，好好利用，你冇槍冇炮，永世都唔好旨意光復到香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"f88e277372192d2a2d933b643cd4b039b431d661","tid":1624033,"uid":75877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:32:21.000Z","msg":"why not both<br />\n<br />\n其實唔出奇<br />\n北京不嬲唔信廣東人"},{"pid":"42995a9a58c18500d1b89de52f0e6620500e56fc","tid":1624033,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"會唔會係為回應調查黑警舖路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界都知只是清算黑警，呢場革命可以收皮，或者冷靜落來<br />\n但黑警一定作反，呢個時候就係解放軍做野時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8de1dcc6b72b85e7c958368497ba1d29a1766fd","tid":1624033,"uid":18024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f88e277372192d2a2d933b643cd4b039b431d661","tid":1624033,"uid":75877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:32:21.000Z","msg":"why not both<br />\n<br />\n其實唔出奇<br />\n北京不嬲唔信廣東人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:37:14.000Z","msg":"呢層認同<br />\n喺共產黨眼中，我覺得同元朝幾似<br />\n北佬唔信上海佬，上海佬唔信廣東人，或者叫南人<br />\n只喺睇吓佢個政治局常委名單，有幾多個喺廣東人？"},{"pid":"dfd553b47362c22f3156e0dc72d20fe3515a5215","tid":1624033,"uid":258687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:37:19.000Z","msg":"歷史已經講左支共對自己人係防得最緊<br />\n<br />\n大把以為自己係忠臣嘅人喺支共眼中只不過係一把用完要消毀罪證嘅屠刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa97ee4dd6d53f22d8bb1ac40fd30ee86f1e288","tid":1624033,"uid":130898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"On9 警察只係步兵"},{"pid":"cfd202682038861bb08310491753dc8894eb029e","tid":1624033,"uid":49994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:41:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53aac642dbca96b95be5e97036eb5837470c63ae","tid":1624033,"uid":207122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:42:38.000Z"